edu.brown.cs.systems.tracingplane.transit_layer

Class TransitLayerCompatibility

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.systems.tracingplane.transit_layer.TransitLayerCompatibility

  • class TransitLayerCompatibility
extends java.lang.Object
    This class just does type checking on Baggage instances to ensure they are compatible with the TransitLayer installed in the current process. In general, Baggage instances should never be created by any transit layer other than the one installed in the current process.
